What are you doing?

58
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:34,370
兄弟，你差点打飞他的脚！
Man, you almost blew his foot off!

59
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:36,449
你不是猎人吧？
You're not a hunter, are you?

60
00:08:37,560 --> 00:08:39,085
不再是了
Not anymore.

61
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:39,448
出了什么事？
What the hell?

62
