真理子小姐

680
01:07:35,160 --> 01:07:36,321
有人来了

681
01:07:36,400 --> 01:07:37,083
真理子？
Mariko?

682
01:07:37,160 --> 01:07:37,968
不说了

683
01:07:38,240 --> 01:07:39,401
真理子？
Mariko?

684
01:07:40,600 --> 01:07:42,364
- 真理子小姐  - 奶奶

685
01:07:42,680 --> 01:07:45,411
真理子小姐，有一树倒在了路边

686
01:07:45,760 --> 01:07:48,604
那个男人能帮上忙

687
01:07:51,320 --> 01:07:53,288
- 茶好了  - 辛苦您了

688
01:07:55,045 --> 01:07:57,011
茶有点儿热，您小心点儿

689
01:08:20,880 --> 01:08:22,530
你还好吧？
Are you okay?

690
01:08:26,400 --> 01:08:27,287
我累了
Tired.

691
01:08:27,840 --> 01:08:29,524
你需要点什么吗？
Do you need something?

692
01:08:31,720 --> 01:08:32,721
不
No.

693
01:08:36,160 --> 01:08:37,356
- 你好啊  - 你好

694
01:08:37,852 --> 01:08:39,532
- 我来个苹果？  - 苹果啊

695
01:08:41,840 --> 01:08:42,966
这个能帮到你
This will help.

696
01:09:34,600 --> 01:09:36,250
是时候了
It's time.

697
01:09:39,120 --> 01:09:40,121
什么？
What?

698
01:09:41,160 --> 01:09:43,891
求你了 收下吧
Please. Take it.

699
01:09:45,400 --> 01:09:46,925
谢谢
Thank you.

700
01:10:05,280 --> 01:10:06,611
不
No.

701
01:10:08,240 --> 01:10:09,810
要握双手
Two hands.

702
01:10:10,280 --> 01:10:14,080
日本的剑要双手握紧
Japanese sword require two hands.

703
01:10:18,880 --> 01:10:21,042
- 像这样？  - 没错
- Like that? - That's it.

704
01:10:23,680 --> 01:10:25,648
真是漂亮，矢志田
It's beautiful, Yashida.

705
01:10:28,560 --> 01:10:29,766
但是我不能收下
But I can't take it.

706
01:10:30,280 --> 01:10:31,566
求你
Please.

707
01:10:32,640 --> 01:10:33,926
谢谢
Thank you.

708
01:10:40,360 --> 01:10:41,521
妥善保管
Keep it safe.

709
01:10:44,440 --> 01:10:46,329
给我妥善保管
Keep it safe for me.

710
01:10:48,920 --> 01:10:51,491
终有一天，我会来取
Someday, I'll come get it.

711
01:10:59,160 --> 01:11:01,003
是时候了
It's time.

712
01:11:47,720 --> 01:11:51,361
事发之时，我在现场
I was here when it happened.

713
01:11:53,840 --> 01:11:56,241
我就是这样认识你的爷爷
It's how I met your grandfather.

714
01:11:56,600 --> 01:11:58,682
我们躲在这里
We hid in there.

715
01:12:00,280 --> 01:12:01,725
我听过你们的故事
I heard the stories.

716
01:12:06,400 --> 01:12:08,050
我的爷爷会说…
My grandfather would say...

717
01:12:08,200 --> 01:12:09,510
这里发生的事见证着
What happened here was proof

718
01:12:09,510 --> 01:12:11,363
世界和平的出现
that everything in the world finds peace.

719
01:12:16,080 --> 01:12:18,082
到最后
Eventually.

720
01:12:22,440 --> 01:12:24,886
人类终能踏上复兴之路
That man can recover from anything.

721
01:12:28,960 --> 01:12:31,486
或许你也一样
Maybe you, too.

722
01:12:37,400 --> 01:12:39,562
你睡得不怎么好
You don't sleep very well.

723
01:12:39,720 --> 01:12:41,722
夜里传来你的呼叫
You call out in the night.

724
01:12:48,320 --> 01:12:49,606
谁是珍？
Who's Jean?

725
01:13:04,640 --> 01:13:06,009
我们该回去了
We should go back.

726
01:13:06,592 --> 01:13:07,371
大雨将至
There's rain coming.

727
01:13:28,120 --> 01:13:29,645
我来烧茶
I'll make tea.

728
01:13:37,800 --> 01:13:39,131
给你
For you.

729
01:14:15,080 --> 01:14:16,570
这样不对
This isn't right.

730
01:14:30,200 --> 01:14:33,488
你要系得像个真正的武士
You need this tied like a proper samurai.

731
01:14:37,480 --> 01:14:39,642
你的爷爷称我为浪人
Your grandfather called me a ronin.

732
01:14:41,080 --> 01:14:43,401
意思是没有主人的武士
A samurai without a master.

733
01:14:45,280 --> 01:14:48,443
他说我命中注定长生不老…
He said I was destined to live forever...

734
01:14:49,560 --> 01:14:52,006
没有意义地活下去
With no reason to live.

735
01:14:56,960 --> 01:14:58,485
他说得对吗？
Was he right?

736
01:14:59,760 --> 01:15:01,091
对
Yes.

737
01:15:06,240 --> 01:15:07,969
现在还是？
Still?

738
01:15:59,160 --> 01:16:00,730
你在干什么？
what are you doing?

739
01:16:05,320 --> 01:16:07,800
不会有好的结果
This isn't going to end well.

740
01:16:12,200 --> 01:16:14,202
你爱上的人都要死去
Everyone you love dies.

741
01:16:34,880 --> 01:16:36,882
Kuzuri.

742
01:16:39,000 --> 01:16:40,684
你知道什么意思吗？
Do you know what that means?

743
01:16:45,360 --> 01:16:47,203
一种动物
An animal.

744
01:16:47,360 --> 01:16:52,605
拥有长爪利牙的凶猛野兽
A fierce creature with long claws and sharp teeth.

745
01:16:54,680 --> 01:16:56,728
它无所畏惧
It fears nothing.

746
01:16:58,520 --> 01:16:59,596
我还是个女孩的时候
When I was a girl,

747
01:17:00,657 --> 01:17:02,570
我做过恶梦
I had nightmares.

748
01:17:03,240 --> 01:17:05,641
我醒来，然后奔向父母
I'd wake up and run to my parents.

749
01:17:06,600 --> 01:17:09,285
我的父亲会发怒
My father would get angry.

750
01:17:09,840 --> 01:17:12,429
别害怕，回到床上去

751
01:17:13,720 --> 01:17:16,803
“回到梦中 面对你的恐惧”
"Go back to sleep. Face your fears."

752
01:17:18,240 --> 01:17:20,766
我的爷爷则不同
My grandfather was different.

753
01:17:21,720 --> 01:17:24,021
他告诉我关于Kuzuri的故事
He told me stories about Kuzuri,

754
01:17:24,544 --> 01:17:25,486
他的朋友
his friend.

755
01:17:26,400 --> 01:17:29,449
就是他在井底认识的那个人
Who he met at the bottom of a well.

756
01:17:31,560 --> 01:17:33,581
他说Kuzuri是天神下凡
He said the Kuzuri was magical

757
01:17:34,367 --> 01:17:36,088
守护他的生命
and saved his life.

758
01:17:38,400 --> 01:17:40,781
他又说Kuzuri会守护我
He said Kuzuri would protect me, too,

759
01:17:41,858 --> 01:17:43,770
在我入睡以后
as I slept in my bed.

760
01:17:52,960 --> 01:17:54,530
谁是珍？
Who's Jean?

761
01:18:02,160 --> 01:18:03,685
她喜欢你吗？
Is she like you?

762
01:18:06,440 --> 01:18:08,442
她发生什么事了？
What happened to her?

763
01:18:09,760 --> 01:18:11,649
她死了
She died.

764
01:18:18,360 --> 01:18:20,124
我杀了她
I killed her.

765
01:18:26,800 --> 01:18:28,723
还有Kuzuri
Along with the Kuzuri.

766
