说话啊，废物？
Where, you piece of shit?

785
01:20:46,360 --> 01:20:48,931
我不会说的，外国佬
I no talk, gaijin.

786
01:20:49,600 --> 01:20:51,489
我不会说的
I never talk.

787
01:20:57,920 --> 01:21:00,127
雇佣你的是谁？
Who hired you?

788
01:21:23,280 --> 01:21:24,964
带我去找森信郎
Take me to Noburo.

789
01:21:25,800 --> 01:21:27,643
罗根… 带我去找他
Logan... Take me to him.

790
01:21:28,560 --> 01:21:29,800
我必须要告诉你一件事
I need to tell you something.

791
01:21:29,960 --> 01:21:31,883
开车 快
Do it. Now.

792
01:21:51,160 --> 01:21:53,083
你留在车里
You wait in the car.

793
01:21:53,560 --> 01:21:55,562
- 罗根  - 什么？
- Logan. - What?

794
01:21:56,400 --> 01:21:58,323
我预见到你的死
I saw you die.

795
01:21:58,480 --> 01:22:00,005
什么？
What?

796
01:22:00,480 --> 01:22:02,244
我预见到你的死
I saw you die.

797
01:22:02,680 --> 01:22:04,682
什么时候？就刚才？
When? Just now?

798
01:22:05,120 --> 01:22:06,849
不久前
Awhile ago.

799
01:22:07,000 --> 01:22:09,890
但是我又看不到完整的画面
But it's not like I get a complete picture.

800
01:22:10,040 --> 01:22:12,327
更像是管中窥豹
More like looking through a keyhole.

801
01:22:13,880 --> 01:22:16,121
但是我的预感没有错过
But I'm always right.

802
01:22:17,000 --> 01:22:20,368
我只能看到一个人一生的一小部分…
All I can see is one part of a person's life...

803
01:22:20,960 --> 01:22:22,530
和他们的死亡
Their death.

804
01:22:23,240 --> 01:22:25,481
如今，我看到你的
And I saw yours.

805
01:22:28,640 --> 01:22:30,563
那么，你看到什么？
So, what did you see?

806
01:22:31,040 --> 01:22:33,157
我看到你的背影
I see you on your back.

807
01:22:33,157 --> 01:22:35,364
周围血迹斑斑
There's blood everywhere.

808
01:22:37,360 --> 01:22:40,409
你手里捧着你的心脏
You're holding your own heart in your hand.

809
01:22:42,480 --> 01:22:44,528
它停止了跳动
It's not beating.

810
01:22:45,320 --> 01:22:46,560
我没有时间听你的鬼话
I don't have time for this shit.

811
01:22:46,920 --> 01:22:48,153
我五岁的时候
When I was five,

812
01:22:48,153 --> 01:22:50,766
就预见到父母的死
I knew how my own parents would die.

813
01:22:53,080 --> 01:22:56,607
然后，我就在后座目睹死亡的发生
Then I watched it happen from the back seat.

814
01:22:59,560 --> 01:23:00,721
看着我
Look at me.

815
01:23:03,840 --> 01:23:05,676
许多人都要我的命
A lot of people have tried to kill me,

816
01:23:05,676 --> 01:23:06,571
但是我还在这
and I'm still here.

817
01:23:08,840 --> 01:23:11,366
但是你如今不同了
But you're different now, aren't you?

818
01:23:12,120 --> 01:23:14,043
他们能伤害你
They can hurt you.

819
01:23:14,200 --> 01:23:16,202
他们能杀死你
They can kill you.

820
